## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="8258a-154">下面的示例演示如何使用连接字符串从数据库中读取数据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8258a-154">The following example shows how to use a connection string to read data from a database.</span></span>  
  
